{
  "stem": "20089.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All the-- all the things that they asked for, I gave it to them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was very moral at the time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and I said that they-- you know, how dare they use it on the black market.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'll give it to them on condition they use it for themselves, but not on the black market.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But of course I was very stupid to think that the things I gave them would be used for anything else but to exchange for things that they would need when they came to a new country.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And a lot of the displaced persons were able to accumulate quite a lot of worldly possessions for their future.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was this one person, I think I mentioned him to you, [?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Misha. ?] Who was a [NON-ENGLISH] during the war.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He came from Russia.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he met his wife in the displaced persons camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they were very, very prominent in the camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they got a lot of stuff, not only from me, from all the personnel.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they were charming and very clever.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And by the time they left for Palestine, they had accumulated many, many, many items which they used once they got to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I would say that anyone who could do that, did it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And now in retrospect, I think that's the way it should have been.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But at the age that I was, and the moral standing that I thought I had, I thought it was disgusting.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a-- a-- a Gordon family.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they came as a family.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they left as a family.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
